e="preserve">Kechun Mao (केचुन माओ) is a Founder of Google Tangi and Lead / Software Engineer at Google.
Early Life and Biography.
Kechun Mao - Coco (केचुन माओ - कोको) was born on november 22th, 1993 in a Shanghai, China. After which Kechun Mao went to America, she studied at Carnegie Mellon University, USA. She then started working in Google as a Software Engineer.
Career and Work.
Kechun Mao is the lead software engineer of [https://area120.google.com Google Area 120], and has been working on software engineers at Google for the last 5 years. She developed apps to assist traders in 2013, in Imc. after that in 2014, she Worked a cool new feature on homepage in Linkdin. From 2015 to 2014, she worked on Photos iOS to make the most delightful Photos management app ever!, From 2017 to 2019, she worked on machine intelligence of [https://www.google.com/photos/about/ Google Photos] to make the most intelligent Photos app ever, From 2011 till now, she is in Project Lead: Tangi in Area 120, where she is the founder of Google tangi app
